{"tid":1543132,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[求集氣]近排識左個人，係唔係時候Move On","createTime":"2019-09-05T05:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T13:57:33.000Z","uid":24647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f0b620614c8ed5de95f44be41c08412b98e822","tid":1543132,"uid":24647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近好似遇到個終於令我想Move On 嘅人。大學四年，我一直鐘意一個女仔，佢話當我係好好好嘅朋友。好怕連朋友都無得做，所以一直將我嘅感覺藏於心底，直到有一日，我終於要被逼放低呢種感覺&hellip;佢突然請我食出Pool飯&hellip;<br />\n        之後我不斷識新朋友，麻醉自己，直到一個月前係TG谷識左個女仔，一個好多女仔嘅谷入面發現到佢咁特別，佢好可愛好純真，第一次見面已經被佢嘅笑容電親。之後慢慢傾計，越傾越埋，不過我好細膽，所以都係每星期群聚先見到面（係啊，我又係收埋係心底啊）。通常我搵佢，佢都會秒回，而佢又話過對我同其他人唔同（特別惡，會笑我、鬧我、打我同搣我），有次仲嗲我講故事哄佢訓。前日約到佢單獨睇戲，咁係唔係代表佢對我都有好感（定我毒撚FF太多）？唉，好驚又變成好好好朋友。<br />\n        大家我今次係咪應該勇敢D試下？求集氣，入黎話我知我應該點做好 呢個係果個谷<a href=\"https://forms.gle/nAKQM5MhvRwpoobg8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FnAKQM5MhvRwpoobg8&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=90492349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/nAKQM5MhvRwpoobg8</a>"},{"pid":"4c339f8e035e923c69ce803577b0944a80a67376","tid":1543132,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBD